                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for improving heat transfer efficiency using steam",
                    "利用蒸汽的传热效率改善方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "Provided is a heat transfer efficiency improvement method capable of effectively improving the heat transfer efficiency by using steam in a low-pH steam system of less than pH 7. A method for improving heat transfer efficiency using steam is characterized in that a sarcosine compound is present in the steam system having a pH of less than 7 in a step for heating an object to be heated by introducing steam into a heat exchanger or a step for liquefying and condensing the steam by bringing the steam into contact with a cooling body. As the sarcosine compound, it is preferable that the sarcosine compound is a long-chain sarcosine compound represented by formula (I). R &lt; 1 &gt; C (= O)-N (CH3)-(CH2) n-COOR &lt; 2 &gt; (I), in the formula (I), R &lt; 1 &gt; is unsaturated or saturated linear chain or branched chain alkyl with the carbon number of 7-24, n is an integer of 0-2, and R &lt; 2 &gt; is a hydrogen atom or a salt forming group."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种在小于pH7的低pH的蒸汽系统内，能有效地改善利用蒸汽的传热效率的传热效率改善方法。一种利用蒸汽的传热效率改善方法，其特征在于，在将蒸汽导入至热交换器来加热被加热物的工序或通过与冷却体接触来使所述蒸汽液化冷凝的工序中，使肌氨酸化合物存在于小于pH7的所述蒸汽系统内。作为肌氨酸化合物，优选为由下述式(I)表示的长链肌氨酸化合物。R1C(＝O)‑N(CH3)‑(CH2)n‑COOR2(I)，式(I)中，R1为碳数为7～24的不饱和或饱和的直链或支链的烃基，n为0～2的整数，R2为氢原子或成盐基。"
                }
            ]
